lead_paragraph: Workers cleared another five tons of dead fish from the shores of a Rio de Janeiro lagoon where Olympic events are due to take place next year.

headline.main: Dead Fish Cleared From Rowing Site in Rio de Janeiro

snippet: Workers cleared another five tons of dead fish from the shores of a Rio de Janeiro lagoon where Olympic events are due to take place next year.
abstract: Five tons of dead fish are cleared from shores of Rio de Janeiro lagoon where 2016 Olympic rowing and canoeing events are scheduled to take place.
